    Visiting the UK from 1 January 2021
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">What you need to know about crossing the UK border and visiting the UK from 1 January 2021.</p>

  </div>
</div>

